title: What happened to influencer Clavicular at Arizona State University fashion show that led to framemogging trend
summary_full: “Clavicular Framemogging” is a viral internet slang phrase that began after influencer Clavicular appeared at an Arizona State University fashion show. A video showing him beside a larger fraternity member led users to joke that he was “framemogged.” The strange sounding phrase quickly turned into memes, proving how fast online culture creates and spreads new slang.
